{"id": "1490327795447103589", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "1121389999737290852", "author_name": "jelly2307", "author_bot": false, "content": "24無凸、リリー無凸、恒常3凸〜、ラモ5凸、オジール6凸、ドール6凸、ロータン3凸です。\n限定の子はカプセルで1凸はできます！", "timestamp": "2026-04-05T12:30:35.386000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["516998769888329749"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1490325683480690759", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1490328658634608851", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "んー、正直、ライカーとハムリンで混沌染めが割と完結してる気がしてるんですよねw", "timestamp": "2026-04-05T12:34:01.186000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1490328699449507991", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "あとはキーチャ回せればよくて", "timestamp": "2026-04-05T12:34:10.917000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1490328910397964299", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "耐久は中々厳しいところがあります。", "timestamp": "2026-04-05T12:35:01.211000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1490329064303628359", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "リリー入れたら結構ガードは出来るのですが、3コスト(3凸で2コスト)の黒沼禁域を多用しないといけないのがめっちゃ苦しいです。", "timestamp": "2026-04-05T12:35:37.905000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1490330418661167275", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "1121389999737290852", "author_name": "jelly2307", "author_bot": false, "content": "なるほど！火力がライカーとハムリンだけでまかなえるか心配だったのですが、2人でなんとか行けそうならよかったです。\n後は連れてく場所に合わせてリリー入れたりしてみますね！\n火力ぶっぱターンはライカーからのハムリン極限でよいでしょうか？", "timestamp": "2026-04-05T12:41:00.809000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["516998769888329749"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1490328658634608851", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1490330789877907579", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "他がちよっと扱いにくいのがあります…\n24ドールをいれるといいかもです!24を1凸して。", "timestamp": "2026-04-05T12:42:29.314000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1490330418661167275", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1490331272982298776", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "混沌染めって色々火力の出し方あるので、ハムリン解放からライカー極限とか、24極限とか色々あるのかなって思います", "timestamp": "2026-04-05T12:44:24.495000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1490331877062606889", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "763468659863584799", "author_name": "sugoitsubasanohaetaop", "author_bot": false, "content": "先日遊んだ染めの編成\n普通に強かった\n雑魚戦はライカーとハムリンの解放をダメージソースにして24は表の解放でダブルオーダーをガンガン回してくのが良い\n札は適当なの突っ込んだけど、やはり知識盛った時の狂気回りが半端じゃないから盛れるだけ盛りたい", "timestamp": "2026-04-05T12:46:48.519000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1490331876836118569", "filename": "Screenshot_20260404-111901.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1392324, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1400058619726266462/1490331876836118569/Screenshot_20260404-111901.png?ex=6a33e8b8&is=6a329738&hm=2797f115047ea016085cc46801d39830b2b73c2b6c320c14c4bb28730b341ee3&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1490332586491510956", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "1121389999737290852", "author_name": "jelly2307", "author_bot": false, "content": "お二人ともありがとうございます！\n24を1凸して入れて、知識もりつつラモンナorドールで試してみようと思います💪 \n\n今までザルバに頼りっきり状態だったので、回し方まで教えていただき助かりました🥹", "timestamp": "2026-04-05T12:49:37.660000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
